data.description: Serene and expansive, this picturesque property spans 10.5 acres. This country home has potential to be an outdoorsmans dream with 3 bedrooms and 2.5 bathrooms, offering a sanctuary of tranquility. Step inside to discover 3178 square feet of living space where the possibilities are endless to ways this house could be made into your home. The heart of the home is an expansive kitchen, perfect for culinary creations and gatherings with loved ones. Its generous proportions invite creativity while providing ample room to indulge in the art of cooking. Adjacent to the kitchen lies an oversized two-car garage, ensuring convenience for all your automotive needs. Beyond the main residence awaits a generously spaced, detached, 1800 SQFT workshop - a haven for those seeking creative pursuits or extra storage space for your possessions. As you wander through this idyllic landscape, be captivated by breathtaking country views. Nature becomes your companion here; deer gracefully roam while wildlife dwells just beyond your doorstep. With vast acreage at your disposal, unleash your inner agriculturist and explore endless possibilities for cultivating thriving gardens or nurturing vineyards under sun-kissed skies. This extraordinary property promises more than just walls; it offers an escape from the ordinary into slowed down, country living. Schedule a showing today!
